Encouraging comments from Claude Puel to L'Equipe about William Saliba<br />
<br />
&quot;It&rsquo;s hard to accept that we sell our best player, a young kid, to help fill the coffers.&quot;

@TransferPodcast has learned that at least two football agents representing multiple #AFC players have been in touch with the hierarchy in the last week or so to discuss Emery&rsquo;s shortcomings: Communication skills, tactics, man management and more.<br />
<br />
@TransferPodcast add that the phrase 'quick to criticize but slow to praise' was mentioned by the agents in reference to how Unai treats his players. He has been described as aloof and distant too. A number of players are concerned about the direction the club with him in charge<br />
<br />
One of the two agent tells @TransferPodcast that the #AFC board are aware of the situation and the shortcomings of Emery but &ldquo;there is no obvious candidate to replace him&rdquo;.
